《北與南蓋茲堡戰役》在商業上非常成功，及至1999年8月已售出二十萬套。當時[[Firaxis_Games|Firaxis Games]]的總裁佐夫·布里格斯曾指這款遊戲「做得非常好」<ref name=igninterview>{{cite web | author=Campbell, Colin | date=1999-08-30 | title=What's Up With ''Sid Meier's Antietam''? | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20020602050912/http://pc.ign.com/articles/069/069973p1.html | url=http://pc.ign.com:80/articles/069/069973p1.html | archive-date=2002-06-02 | work=[[IGN|IGN]]}}</ref> 。評論網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上亦獲得了「大眾讚賞」評級<ref name="mc"/>。 

《北與南蓋茲堡戰役》是1997年由{{link-en|互動藝術與科學學院|Academy of Interactive Arts＆Sciences}}頒授的「年度最佳策略遊戲獎」的決賽入圍者<ref>{{cite web |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19980615090128/http://www.interactive.org/html/award/awardupdate.htm |url=http://www.interactive.org:80/html/award/awardupdate.htm |title=The Award; Award Updates |publisher=[[Academy_of_Interactive_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences]] |archive-date=1998-06-15}}</ref><ref name=aias1997>{{cite web |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19980615090115/http://www.interactive.org/html/award/awardwin98.htm |url=http://www.interactive.org:80/html/award/awardwin98.htm |title=The Award; Award Updates |publisher=[[Academy_of_Interactive_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences]] |archive-date=1998-06-15}}</ref>，亦獲[[遊戲開發者大會|遊戲開發者大會]]的「最佳戰略/戰爭遊戲特別獎」提名<ref name=cgdc1998>{{cite web | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19990429031108/http://www.ogr.com/specials/cgdc98/08spotlight.html | url=http://www.ogr.com/specials/cgdc98/08spotlight.html | title=Spotlight Award Winners | date=1998-05-08 | author=Jensen, Chris | work=Online Gaming Review | publisher=[[Computer_Games_Magazine|Strategy Plus, Inc.]] | archive-date=1999-04-29}}</ref>。雖然最終皆未能獲獎，但本遊戲仍被《電腦遊戲世界》、《電腦遊戲策略增強版》和《GameSpot》評為1997年的最佳電腦戰爭遊戲，電腦遊戲世界甚至將稱「史上最好的設計師回歸了」，並寫道「這遊戲真的會玩到約翰行軍回家<ref name=aias1997>{{cite web |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19980615090115/http://www.interactive.org/html/award/awardwin98.htm |url=http://www.interactive.org:80/html/award/awardwin98.htm |title=The Award; Award Updates |publisher=[[Academy_of_Interactive_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences]] |archive-date=1998-06-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19990429031108/http://www.ogr.com/specials/cgdc98/08spotlight.html | url=http://www.ogr.com/specials/cgdc98/08spotlight.html | title=Spotlight Award Winners | date=1998-05-08 | author=Jensen, Chris | work=Online Gaming Review | publisher=[[Computer_Games_Magazine|Strategy Plus, Inc.]] | archive-date=1999-04-29}}</ref><ref name=gamespot1997>{{cite web |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010208121409/http://www.gamespot.com/features/awards97/cont.html |url=http://www.gamespot.com:80/features/awards97/cont.html |title=Best & Worst Awards 1997 |author=Staff |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |archive-date=2001-02-08  }}</ref><ref name=cgwpremier1997>{{cite journal | author=Staff | journal=[[Computer_Gaming_World|Computer Gaming World]] | title=''CGW'' Presents The Best & Worst of 1997 |date=March 1998 | issue=164 | pages=74–77, 80, 84, 88, 89 }}</ref><ref name=cgmawards1997>{{cite web|author=Staff |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050206152953/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/009/194/1997_cgsp_awards.html |url=http://www.cdmag.com:80/articles/009/194/1997_cgsp_awards.html |title=The winners of the 1997 ''Computer Games'' Awards |date=1998-01-19 |work=[[Computer_Games_Magazine|Computer Games Strategy Plus]] |archive-date=2005-02-06}}</ref>。」 

Next Generation亦評價了該遊戲的PC版本，五顆星中給予了五顆，並表示「《北與南蓋茲堡戰役》是Firaxis最出色的首創產品」，不僅使以前的模擬遊戲黯然失色，還可擊敗現時大多數的實時策略遊戲<ref name="NG">{{cite magazine|title=Finals|magazine=[[Next_Generation_(magazine)|Next Generation]]|issue=37|publisher=[[Future_US|Imagine Media]]|date=January 1998|page=158}}</ref>。 

1998年，《北與南蓋茲堡戰》役贏得了最佳戰略電腦遊戲的起源獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.originsgamefair.com/awards/1997/list-of-winners  |title=Origins Award Winners (1997)  |publisher=Academy of Adventure Gaming Arts & Design  |accessdate=2008-06-03  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080331064621/http://www.originsgamefair.com/awards/1997/list-of-winners  |archive-date=2008-03-31 }}</ref>
。

== 影響 ==
《北與南蓋茲堡戰役》出現了各種玩家自創的遊戲模組。玩家可以自定制服、地圖、背景音樂和兵種。由於本遊戲在模組設計上適合套用到歷史上的其他戰爭，因此深受戰爭迷歡迎，製作出其他著名戰役的改編版本，例如[[弗雷德里克斯堡戰役|弗雷德里克斯堡戰役]]，[[第一次馬納沙斯之役|第一次馬納沙斯之役]]，[[半島會戰|半島會戰]]等<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.moddb.com/games/sid-meiers-gettysburg|title=ModDB遊戲介紹|access-date=2021-01-22|archive-date=2022-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220525125310/https://www.moddb.com/games/sid-meiers-gettysburg}}</ref>。本遊戲的模組亦被{{link-en|BreakAway Games|BreakAway Games}}用來製作《滑鐵盧：拿破崙的最後一戰》<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.breakawaygames.com/games/waterloo/|title=BreakAway Games官方網頁介紹|access-date=2021-01-22|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128065432/https://www.breakawaygames.com/games/waterloo/}}</ref>。 

[[Firaxis_Games|Firaxis Games]]後推出了續作《{{link-en|北與南安提頓戰役|Sid Meier's Antietam!}}》<ref>{{cite journal | author=Staff | journal=[[Computer_Gaming_World|Computer Gaming World]] | title=The 2000 Premier Awards; The Very Best of a Great Year in Gaming |date=March 2000 | issue=188 | pages=69–75, 78–81, 84–90 }}</ref>。

